{% assign test_style = 'color: #3A3F46; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;' %}
{% markdown p_style: test_style %}

Dear {{ contact.name }}

We are happy to announce the release of version 5.4.1 of EasyQuery.NET together with version 6.1.0 of EasyQuery.JS! 

With these updates, you get a lot of changes both on the client-side and server-side parts: new data grid, new "facets" panel, pivot tables, and other great features together with the improved performance and fixed bugs.  
 
For more information please refer to the [Release Notes](https://korzh.com/easyquery/docs/release-notes/easyquery-net-5-4-1-easyquery-js-6-1-0) and the [Changelog](https://korzh.com/easyquery/docs/changelog).

The sample projects for the new version are available on the GitHub as usual: https://github.com/easyquery

--    
Kind regards, EasyQuery team.
https://korzh.com/easyquery

{% endmarkdown %}

